{"tid":1544704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[港交所+機場=左右春袋。治權=成抽野] 今次要將中共成抽野閹左佢！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-05T15:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T03:41:46.000Z","uid":139095,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc408849a2f2611a0b7a2d16db7b580ad499c19","tid":1544704,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:55:00.000Z","msg":"最近美國國會提哂水，香港呢一場係關於香港管治及主權正當性既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自治運動</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n詳情其他巴打有講<br />\n<br />\n美國國會提晒水：香港人需要向世界宣告──這是一場香港自治運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543035</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n雖然我信連登咁多人已經知「反送中」唔止「反送中」!<br />\n但我地要衝出<span style=\"color: red;\">同温層</span>，將呢個話題推上水面。<br />\n俾彈藥自己同西方民主國家，特別係美國、英國、台灣。<br />\n<br />\n本人察覺到口號對於 跟得唔太貼、<span style=\"color: red;\">冇上連登既市民</span><strong>非常</strong>重要。<br />\n<br />\n好似「五大訴求，缺一不可」咁，係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">極好</span>既口號，令<strong>任何人</strong>都知唔可以因為條例撤回而收貨。<br />\n<br />\n所以好既文宣口號就代表住成個運動既<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大方向</span></span>，好似共產黨大躍進既三面紅旗咁。<br />\n<br />\n而口號更係代替大台領導群眾既必要工具，對香港而家冇大台既流水式抗爭非常重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港人治港</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">高度自治</span></span>作為新既口號<br />\n<br />\n將抗爭帶到關於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">&quot;治權&quot;</span></span>既新階段<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">將中共成抽子孫根連根拔，閹左佢！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n(你都可以用&quot;一國兩制&quot;做口號，中立易入口d，雖然本人唔太鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港人治港，勢不可擋</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">普選自治，港人話事</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自古以來，中共靠害</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港內政，中共靜靜</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港內政，撥亂反正</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>小弟不才，求文宣組及各路好手獻詞</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113c69808a87ef64f60c53cf40a34e37b85d1fe2","tid":1544704,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:55:11.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8e06196461e1f980b89869c8bfa21355d4906f30","tid":1544704,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:57:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1f8119a4a550f37c8b25df5afd72aafc785e1f0","tid":1544704,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:57:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99d67b329b2e023e914a65274a004c10d9e80c67","tid":1544704,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:57:23.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"0b0df11100a8a6bb02d1a83e9bc0d2f6ed39e1e8","tid":1544704,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:58:09.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"3aef25cf8b54bc4e76d66d23abde7a03ea715c32","tid":1544704,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:58:19.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"368005499b4e73a1dce9197eddb03170d325b69d","tid":1544704,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:59:27.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"cb9832bd0932cfb454e9ea83b2c62cfc1944bfb2","tid":1544704,"uid":43311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:59:31.000Z","msg":"831 CCTV<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n907 機場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n908  美領 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc352ce68441485f69ff78017e069026676fb0a9","tid":1544704,"uid":139